font-family: "times new roman";">此处用大写的 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>Λ </em></span>表示惯性矩比，以避免与椭球的半轴比 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>λ</em></span><em> </em>混淆。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">3</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">．凯尔文问题</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">   </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">英国物理学家<span style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333; background: white;">汤姆森 (Thomson,W.) 或称</span>凯尔文爵士 (Lord Kelvin)（图 2）于 1877 年在薄壁球形充液腔的旋转实验中，发现其自旋运动处于临界稳定状态<sup style="font-family: "times new roman";">[1]</sup>。当陀螺外形稍趋扁平时旋转轴保持稳定，而稍趋细长即出现强烈不稳定现象。为解释此现象曾引起数学界和物理学界热议。1880 年格林希尔 (Greenhill,G.)，1885 年茹可夫斯基 (Rhukovsky,N.E.) 先后給出理论解释。即使到了上世纪，仍吸引了 Poincaré,  Chetayev,  Parks 等数学家的兴趣。<br></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="309" height="389" style="width: 309px; height: 389px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图</span><span style="font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2   </span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">凯尔文</span><span style="font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">(Lord Kelvin, 1824-1907)</span><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><br></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">应用上述离散化方法可对凯尔文问题作出简明的解释。为此将</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"> </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">z, w</span></em></span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"> </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">的指数形式特解</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"> </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">z = Z</span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">e<sup>i<em>s</em></sup></span><em><sup>τ</sup></em>, <em>w </em><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">= W</span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">e<sup>i<em>s</em></sup></span><em><sup>τ </sup></em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">代入复数方程组(21)，导出以 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">s</span></em></span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"> </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">为变量的频率方程：</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">                                         <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/08/100346hjut43eero41e1og.png" title alt="欧拉22.png" width="337" height="41" style="width: 337px; height: 41px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">                                        (23)<br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman',serif"></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">根据此方程的根为纯虚数或实数的条件判断，自旋充液刚体的一次近似稳定性条件为：</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman";">                                          <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/08/100705fbo3wutbouoor9uo.png" title alt="欧拉23.png" width="380" height="77" style="width: 380px; height: 77px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">                                    (24)<br></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">设主刚体为薄壁壳体，忽略其质量仅考虑流体团的质量。充液腔为旋转椭球形，其主惯性矩等参数为</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"></span>                               <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/08/100953c6whq633nkwhnuz3.png" title alt="欧拉24.png" width="407" height="70" style="width: 407px; line-height: 150%;">= 4</span><em>πρa</em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><sub>1</sub><sup>4</sup></span><em> a</em><sub>3</sub>/15</span> <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">。代入式 (22)，得到</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">                                                    <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/08/101513wr6l8pfw0sygar6l.png" title alt="欧拉25.png" width="276" height="80" style="width: 276px; text-align: justify;"><span style=";line-height:150%;font-family:宋体"></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">从而解释了凯尔文实验得出的 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman";
